pg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Dua-Lipa-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>表示，她即将推出的“充满迷幻流行音乐”的专辑的灵感来自于<a href="/artists/primal-scream">《Primal Scream》</a>和<a href="/artists/massive-attack">《Massive Attack》</a>等歌曲。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="121" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/dua-lipa-houdini-track-review-lyrics-3534865"><b>杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa) 的《胡迪尼》暗示了一个受驯服黑斑羚影响的时代，您将不想逃离</b></a></li></ul><p>这位流行歌手此前在接受<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/166025/Dua-Lipa-drops-Houdini-and-reveals-rest-of-album-is-quite-different" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>iHeartRadio</em></a>采访时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-says-new-album-is-quite-different-to-houdini-but-very-psychedelic-3536244">公开了这张专辑的声音</a>，并表示新唱片将有“迷幻的主线”。</p><p> “专辑中的所有其他歌曲都非常不同，但总体上它们确实有一个非常迷幻的主线，”她说。 “《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/dua-lipa-houdini-track-review-lyrics-3534865">Houdini</a> 》有如此多的电子音乐多样性，但同时它也有很多有趣的乐器，而且感觉也非常有机……这就是我真正想在专辑中传达的东西。”</p><p>现在，在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/dua-lipa-third-album-influences-dating-life-acting-1234945422/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>杂志的新简介中，这位“Dance The Night Away”歌手透露了她的唱片的更多影响。</p><p>在简介中，记者 Brittany Spanos 写道，Lipa 将这张专辑称为“对英国锐舞文化注入迷幻流行音乐的致敬”，其灵感来自 Primal Scream 1991 年的 LP“Screamadelica”和 Massive Attack。这张专辑的其他灵感包括<a href="/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>和<a href="/artists/blur">Blur</a>等英伦流行音乐传奇人物，以及<a href="/artists/moby">Moby</a>和<a href="/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a>等 90 年代摇滚和电子音乐人。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2Ao6RcspB2/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546