</p><p>她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-olivia-rodrigo-and-dua-lipa-to-perform-at-grammys-2024-3571443">在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼上表演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-says-new-psychedelic-pop-infused-album-is-inspired-by-primal-scream-and-massive-attack-3571849">Dua Lipa 表示，新专辑“充满迷幻流行”的灵感来自于《Primal Scream》和《Massive Attack》，该专辑</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
